rows.name:
On your journey, have you ever seen
an incredibly strong monster, mo?

rows.label: tlk4235012502_msg0002
rows.name:
They're so strong that someone, somewhere,
gave them a special name at some point, mo.

rows.label: tlk4235012502_msg0003
rows.name:
If you want to test your strength, I won't stop
you, but... the basic rule is to run, mo.
